    "description": "We at Divi's Laboratories International Enterprises are looking for an experienced Radiologist based out of Faridabad. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Divi's Laboratories International Enterprises:\nDivi's Laboratories International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Faridabad, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Divi's Laboratories International Enterprises!",
